OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FA jury has concluded that a police
OL,7,Fofficer's late night road pursuit of a
OL,8,Fyoung couple's van contributed to a
OL,9,Fcrash which claimed both of their
OL,10,Flives.
OL,12,FThey also concluded excess alcohol
OL,13,Falongside cocaine and ketamine in the
OL,14,Fdriver's system was a significant
OL,15,Ffactor in the crash.
OL,17,FRyan Duffy, 24, and 20-year-old Ellie
OL,18,FMarsden were found dead inside a
OL,19,FCitroen Berlingo at around 7:30am on 5
OL,20,FSeptember 2021.
