OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FThe van had left a country lane in
OL,7,Fdarkness, in the early hours and
OL,8,Fcollided with a tree several miles
OL,9,Ffrom the village of Kings Meaburn,
OL,10,Fnear Appleby-in-Westmorland.
OL,12,FAn inquest into their deaths heard the
OL,13,Fcouple had travelled from their
OL,14,FGreater Manchester homes to Appleby at
OL,15,F10pm on 4 September.
OL,17,FThey booked into a hotel at the town's
OL,18,Fhistoric castle for the night, with Mr
OL,19,FDuffy telling a hotel's duty manager:
OL,20,F"I just want to make her happy with a
OL,21,Fnight away."
