OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FThe couple visited the nearby town
OL,7,Fcentre Hare & Hounds pub for two
OL,8,Fhours. At around 12:30am, CCTV footage
OL,9,Fcaptured them returning to a parked
OL,10,FCitroen Berlingo van, which drove on
OL,11,Fto a main town road heading towards
OL,12,Fthe castle.
OL,14,FTheir presence was also noted by PC
OL,15,FCraig Stevenson, a standard response
OL,16,Fofficer on patrol who decided to
OL,17,Ffollow and monitor the van's movements.
OL,19,FHe watched as the driver went the
OL,20,Fwrong way along a one-way street, the
OL,21,Fcourt heard.
