OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FThe jury has heard that PC Stevenson
OL,7,Fcontinued following, seeking to stop
OL,8,Fthe car and speak with the driver. His
OL,9,Fown Ford Transit vehicle data showed
OL,10,Fhe repeatedly travelled above the
OL,11,Fspeed limit both in Appleby and then
OL,12,Fout on to rural country roads as he
OL,13,Fattempted, unsuccessfully, to catch up
OL,14,Fwith the Berlingo.
OL,16,FBoth vehicles turned onto a country
OL,17,Flane known as Long Rigg. At that
OL,18,Fstage, PC Stevenson lost sight of the
OL,19,Fvan. He stopped and sent a radio
OL,20,Fmessage to his control room.
