OL,6,FHe was 170 metres from where the
OL,7,Fcrashed Berlingo was later found.
OL,9,F"Just had a vehicle make off from me
OL,10,Fon the back roads from Appleby," the
OL,11,Fofficer reported, before turning
OL,12,Faround.
OL,14,FHe had never managed to log the
OL,15,Fregistration number of the Berlingo,
OL,16,Fnor the vehicle's make, during a four-
OL,17,Fminute journey. He told jurors the
OL,18,Fopportunity to activate blue lights to
OL,19,Fattempt a safe stoppage did not arise.
