OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FPC Stevenson confirmed he was trained
OL,7,Fto follow and stop vehicles but not to
OL,8,Fengage in any pursuit which, he
OL,9,Fexplained, was a "high risk activity"
OL,10,Ffor any officer or people in a subject
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,FAt no stage, he told jurors, did he
OL,14,Fbelieve he was involved in a
OL,15,F"spontaneous pursuit", as defined by
OL,16,FCollege of Policing policy. This
OL,17,Fdictates that if a driver is aware of
OL,18,Fpolice presence, fails to stop and a
OL,19,Fpursuit begins, a non-trained pursuit
OL,20,Fofficer must immediately inform a
OL,21,Fcontrol room and disengage.
