OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,F"I didn't believe it was a pursuit,"
OL,7,FPC Stevenson told assistant coroner
OL,8,FJoseph Hart, during the inquest.
OL,10,FAfter listening to evidence over the
OL,11,Fcourse of a week, a jury concluded, on
OL,12,Fthe balance of probabilities, that Mr
OL,13,FDuffy had become aware of the
OL,14,Fofficer's presence while driving out
OL,15,Fof Appleby.
OL,17,FMr Duffy took evasive action, the jury
OL,18,Ffound, unanimously, resulting in a
OL,19,Fspontaneous pursuit.
