OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FThe 11-strong jury concluded on
OL,7,FTuesday (18 March) that there were a
OL,8,Fnumber of factors which contributed to
OL,9,Fthe deaths of Mr Duffy and Miss
OL,10,FMarsden in the collision.
OL,12,FOne was excess alcohol, with a post-
OL,13,Fmortem reading from Mr Duffy's
OL,14,Fbloodstream showing he was between two
OL,15,Fand three times the legal drink-drive
OL,16,Flimit; along with other intoxicants,
OL,17,Fcocaine and ketamine also being found
OL,18,Fin his system.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/14
