OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FAnother factor, jurors found, was
OL,7,Fdriver error, with Mr Duffy, of Ashton-
OL,8,Fin-Makerfield, failing to negotiate a
OL,9,Fbend on which he crashed. A third
OL,10,Ffactor was the fact that neither he
OL,11,Fnor Miss Marsden, of Golborne, had
OL,12,Fbeen wearing seat belts.
OL,14,FAnd a fourth, the court heard, was PC
OL,15,FStevenson following the van.
OL,17,F"On the balance of probabilities the
OL,18,Fpolice officer was engaged in a
OL,19,Fspontaneous pursuit of Ryan, and this
OL,20,Fcontributed to causing the crash,"
OL,21,Fconcluded jurors.
