OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FRelatives of Miss Marsden wept as the
OL,7,Fconclusions were delivered by a jury
OL,8,Fforeman.
OL,10,FKelly Kennedy, Ellie's mum, said: "We
OL,11,Fwould like to thank the Coroner and
OL,12,Fthe jury for their thorough and
OL,13,Fdetailed approach. The conclusions
OL,14,Fthey have reached have vindicated all
OL,15,Fthat I have been fighting for over the
OL,16,Flast three and a half years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
