OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,F"The daily pain we have had to endure
OL,7,Fever since losing our beautiful
OL,8,Fdaughter Ellie is crippling. No parent
OL,9,Fshould have to go through losing a
OL,10,Fchild and especially in such horrific
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,F"Ellie is and was the most loving,
OL,14,Fkind and caring daughter, who had her
OL,15,Fwhole life ahead of her. She was more
OL,16,Fthan just a daughter, she was my best
OL,17,Ffriend and the best friend of her
OL,18,Fheartbroken sister Chloe. Our lives
OL,19,Fare completely shattered without her
OL,20,Fhere in our arms and we will ache for
OL,21,Fher for the rest of our lives."
