OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FCoroner Mr Hart offered his sympathies
OL,7,Fto the loved ones of care assistant
OL,8,FMiss Marsden and Mr Duffy, a United
OL,9,FUtilities leakage engineer.
OL,11,F"There is literally nothing I can say
OL,12,Fto diminish your loss and the tragedy
OL,13,Fof your loss," he said.
