OL,3,CJury comes to verdict in inquest into
OL,4,Ccrash which killed couple
OL,6,FA statement from Cumbria Police said:
OL,7,F"The constabulary has supported the
OL,8,Fcoronial process and respects the
OL,9,Ffindings and conclusions of the
OL,10,Finquest today. We will now review
OL,11,Fthese and consider any actions,
OL,12,Flearning, training or changes in
OL,13,Fprocedures that need to take place.
OL,15,F"This incident was referred to the
OL,16,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,17,F(IOPC) following the tragic incident
OL,18,Fin 2021, who returned the
OL,19,Finvestigation back to the
OL,20,Fconstabulary. We will contact the IOPC
OL,21,Fregarding today's conclusions.
